    Displayed as a DialogFragment on top of activity_creator_item_card.xml.
    Shows three graphs (Adds, Removes, Reviews over time) + average rating number.

    GRAPHS: Uses MPAndroidChart library (com.github.PhilJay:MPAndroidChart).
    Add to build.gradle (app level):
        dependencies {
            implementation 'com.github.PhilJay:MPAndroidChart:v3.1.0'
        }
    Add to settings.gradle (or build.gradle project level):
        repositories {
            maven { url 'https://jitpack.io' }
        }

    VIEW IDs:
    - @+id/tvMetricsTitle     — "Purchase Metrics" heading
    - @+id/tvAvgRatingLabel   — "Average Rating" label
    - @+id/tvAvgRatingValue   — numeric average e.g. "3.5 / 5"
    - @+id/tvAddsLabel        — "Adds over time" label
    - @+id/chartAdds          — LineChart for adds
    - @+id/tvRemovesLabel     — "Removes over time" label
    - @+id/chartRemoves       — LineChart for removes
    - @+id/tvReviewsLabel     — "Reviews over time" label
    - @+id/chartReviews       — LineChart for reviews count
    - @+id/btnCloseMetrics    — closes the dialog

